{"tid":1794434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中共如何用民主騙人 | 明居正「透視中國","createTime":"2019-12-23T06:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T07:57:05.000Z","uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"66f5a78782028094685d5781247d595d081362ba","tid":1794434,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:06:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ToDk26g3-LI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DToDk26g3-LI&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwT2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=691d1354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ToDk26g3-LI</a><br />\n值得一睇<br />\n《新華日報》1941年6月2日<br />\n統制思想，以求安於一尊;箝制言論，以使莫敢予毒，這是中國過去專制時代的愚民政策，這是歐洲中古黑暗時代的現象，這是法西斯主義的辦法，這是 促使文化的倒退，決不適於今日民主的世界，尤不適於必須力求進步的中國&hellip;言論出版的自由，是民主政治的基本要件，沒有言論出版的自由便不可能有真正的民主，不民主便不能團結統一，不能爭取勝利，不能建國，也不能在戰後的世界中享受永久和平的幸福&hellip;新聞自由，是民主的標幟;沒有新聞自由，便沒有真正的民主。反之，民主自由是新聞自由的基礎，沒有政治的民主而要得到 真正的新聞自由，決不可 能。<br />\n<br />\n《劉少奇選集》上卷第172-177頁<br />\n<br />\n共產黨要奪取政權，要建立共產黨的&ldquo;一黨專政&ldquo;。這是一種惡意的造謠與誣衊。共產黨反對國民黨的&ldquo;一黨專政&rdquo;，但幷不要建立共產黨的&ldquo;一黨專政&rdquo;。 目前推行民主政治，主要關鍵在於結束一黨治國。&hellip;&hellip;因為此問題一日不解決，則國事勢必包攬於一黨之手;才智之士，無從引進;良好建議，不能實行。因而所謂民主，無論搬出何種花樣，只是空有其名而已。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《新華日報》1939年2月25日<br />\n要徹底地、充分地、有效地實行普選制，使人民能在實際上，享有&ldquo;普通&ldquo;、&ldquo;平等&ldquo;的選舉權、被選舉權，則必須如中山先生所說，在選舉以前，&ldquo;保障各地方團體及人民有選舉之自由，有提出議案及宣傳、討論之自由。&ldquo;也就是&ldquo;確定人民有集會、結社、言論、出版的完全自由權。&ldquo;否則，所謂選舉權，仍不過是紙上的權利罷了。<br />\n<br />\n又唔見你比香港有普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n<br />\n《新華日報》1943年9月15日社論<br />\n二十年來，尤其是最近幾年，我們天天見的是&ldquo;只許州官放火，不許百姓點燈。&ldquo;政府所頒布的法令，其是否為人民着想，姑置不論。最使人憤慨的是連這樣的法，政府幷未遵守。政府天天要人民守法，而政府自己卻天天違法。這樣的作風，和民主二字相距十萬八千里!所以民主雲雲者是真是假，我們卑之無甚高論，第一步先看政府所發的那些空頭民主支票究竟兌現了百分之幾?如果已經寫在白紙上的黑字尚不能兌現，還有什麼話可說?所以在政治協商會議開會以前，我們先要請把那些諾言來兌現，從這一點起碼應做的小事上，望政府示人民以大信。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你睇完有冇覺得可笑.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05611ebbbcbcc10af656445e889ef78c0207718","tid":1794434,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:08:02.000Z","msg":"呢段好適合香港<br />\n共產黨幾時找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《新華日報》1939年2月25日<br />\n要徹底地、充分地、有效地實行普選制，使人民能在實際上，享有&ldquo;普通&ldquo;、&ldquo;平等&ldquo;的選舉權、被選舉權，則必須如中山先生所說，在選舉以前，&ldquo;保障各地方團體及人民有選舉之自由，有提出議案及宣傳、討論之自由。&ldquo;也就是&ldquo;確定人民有集會、結社、言論、出版的完全自由權。&ldquo;否則，所謂選舉權，仍不過是紙上的權利罷了。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8feefff0a7af853a171ea1f38b211ba4994e10b","tid":1794434,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dbe5a476722fc5c4bf499f4f5f101d34bbc3bd36","tid":1794434,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"be908e5a64578b17a77ab3685804fae8a61af550","tid":1794434,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n明居正講中共黨史 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b72a3569ae383a70be9cdb12732926366758dd","tid":1794434,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:14:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"da1bea7aae992dd669c1a3ab2e603c03d8e904c1","tid":1794434,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:14:53.000Z","msg":"教下大家應該用返中共既文宣黎做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f747451e5d0c16baced1937a73deabcf40e69e","tid":1794434,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:18:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c3591b63a21dc2332ee2d7467e6dc7ff5f2143a0","tid":1794434,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"957a0a123888aa6a65957c8a53ab3103db2a2f9e","tid":1794434,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525ab9cbbb77d1492a14c540f4dec490f83190d9","tid":1794434,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:27:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[我終於搵到FC撚嘅歸屬地] 已經整好左個搜尋器，而家要大家俾意見想要有咩類別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"46b95db4f921c3340371f486ed17df2546645c98","tid":1794434,"uid":186074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"明朝清朝共朝"},{"pid":"8d705a5dc578795e2ea5b266c4cac17a79dfdb2c","tid":1794434,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be908e5a64578b17a77ab3685804fae8a61af550","tid":1794434,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n明居正講中共黨史 <img src=\"/assets/faces/no